    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's probably just a bit of inflammation from the procedure right? i mean, its just a tiny little cyst. would it be okay if i just put a warm compress on it a few times a day and maybe some of that neosporin stuff from the chemist to keep it clean? i'm sure that would clear it up pretty quick without needing a whole doctor's visit.",
