      "content": "but i literally can't take time off work right now to go to a clinic, and it feels like such a hassle for just a small nick. i've seen people do this all the time with minor cuts. if i just keep it clean with the warm water and use the antibiotic cream, isn't that basically what a doctor would tell me to do anyway? surely it's fine to just monitor it at home for a day or two before making a big deal out of it?",
